title: The Best of The Three Tenors (2002 CD) (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Hi folks, here's the truly greatest "Three Tenors" for you, including
of course Jose Carreras Placido Domingo and Luciano Pavarotti
This is the music of their 2002 CD - "The best of The Three Tenors"

enjoy and please seek kindly for all

Michael Rizzo Chessman
